nodes.text: Swift Return was a retrofitted Consular-class cruiser that served as a frigate in the Galactic Republic's Navy. Swift Return was destroyed in battle with the acclaimed Admiral Trench prior to the Battle of Christophsis of 22 BBY.

Swift Return first appeared in "Cat and Mouse," an episode of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series' second season which aired on March 26 2010, as a computer readout. Its name was written in Aurebesh in the episode, and the English translation was confirmed in the corresponding episode guide on StarWars.com.
